<p><strong>Senses</strong> darkvision 30 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> telepathy 30 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 0 (10 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Illumination.</em></strong> As a bonus action, the cranium rat can shed dim light from its brain in a 5-foot radius or extinguish the light.</p>

<p><strong><em>Telepathic Shroud.</em></strong> The cranium rat is immune to any effect that would sense its emotions or read its thoughts, as well as to all divination spells.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 1 piercing damage.</p>

